### Test your deployed Travel API
### Replace YOUR_RAILWAY_URL with your actual Railway URL (e.g., https://your-app.up.railway.app)

@baseUrl = https://steppia-travel-production.up.railway.app

### 1. Health Check - Test MongoDB Connection
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/mongo

### 2. Get Swagger UI Documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger

### 3. List All Tours
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours

### 4. Get Tour by Slug (replace 'tour-slug' with an actual slug)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tours/tour-slug

